{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_07_01",
  "title": "miho 1話 容赦なく刈りますから",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "う、うーん……前髪はこんな感じか……？\n……ちょっと切り過ぎたような",
      "translations": {
        "en": "U-Umm… Is this how the bangs should look…?\n…I think I cut it off a little too much",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_scissor-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1733.3333332999998,
          "startTime": 2.5333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_scissor-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5000,
          "startTime": 11.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "気を取り直して後ろ髪も\n……見えないから切り辛いな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Get ahold of myself and the back of my head\n…It's hard to cut because I can't see it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2533.3333334000017,
          "startTime": 16.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n今度のヘアケア用品のCM撮影について一点――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san\nA little about the upcoming hair care products CM shoot—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_scissor-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3300.0003814999986,
          "startTime": 20.9000003815
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "わわっ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.9000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "なんですか、突然大きな声を出して\nあ……なるほど、そういうことですか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you doing‚ suddenly make a loud noise\nAh… I see‚ that's what it is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ゆ、床に大量の髪の毛が……\n結構バッサリいってしまったぞ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-So much hair on the floor…\nI cut it pretty short…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……私のせいじゃないですから\n大体、こんな所で髪を切る方が悪いんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's not my fault\nWhat the‚ it's your fault for cutting your hair in a place like this",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.2686036788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "確かにそうですね……最近忙しくて髪を切りに行く\n時間がなくて……すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true… I've been so busy lately that I haven't had time to\ngo to the hair salon… I'm sorry",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.7407381907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "いくら時間がなくても自分で髪を切るなんて\nアイドルのマネージャーとして恥ずかしくないんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if you're busy‚ you shouldn't cut your own hair\nIsn't that embarrassing for an idol's manager",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、前髪もオン眉パッツンになっていますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ your bangs are already very short",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "後ろ髪が多少……短くなったところで\n大して惨状は変わらないですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if the back of your hair gets a little… shorter‚\nit doesn’t change the fact that it’s a tragedy",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.126762405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、その頭でCM撮影に来ないで下さいね。大手化粧品\nメーカーさんに私の品性まで疑われてしまいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ please don't come to the CM shoot with that hairstyle. The major cosmetics\nmaker will start to doubt my professionalism",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.6659624204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そこまで酷いことになっているのか俺の頭は……\nどうしよう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-Has my head really gotten that bad…\nWhat should I do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……仕方ありませんね。私のせいではありませんが\n特別に美容院を紹介して差し上げます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… there's no other way. It's not my fault‚\nbut I'll recommend a special beauty salon for you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "そこでその斬新な頭を整えてもらって来て下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please go there and get that unique hairstyle fixed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――美容院",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Hair Salon",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_restroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "restroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.5333337029
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_restroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "restroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.5333337029
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "こ、ここがmihoさん行きつけの美容院か……\nオシャレ過ぎてなんだか落ち着かないな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-This is the beauty salon that miho-san goes to…\nIt's too stylish‚ I feel so uncomfortable…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_restroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "restroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.7666695913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと。あんまりキョロキョロしないで下さい\nみっともない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me. Don't look around so much\nIt's ugly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "あと、知り合いだと思われたら恥ずかしいので\n半径十メートル以内に入らないで下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And‚ I'd be embarrassed if they thought we know each other\nDo not enter within 10m of me",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5133.3333334000035,
          "startTime": 120.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_restroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "restroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.733336258
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "は、はぁ……。あ、今日の担当さんですか？\nえっと、軽く整えて清潔感が――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-Haa… Ah‚ are you stylist for today?\nUmm‚ Lightly tidy up and clean――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_restroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "restroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.7666685741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは黙っていて下さい\n私がオーダーしますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ please just be quiet\nI'll order it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.9570913645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_restroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "restroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.8666685741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。前も後ろも切り過ぎて変になっているので\nそれをカバーする形で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes. It looks weird because too much of the front and back are cut off\nIn a form that covers it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね、じゃあそんな感じで……\nよろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ so that's how it feels…\nI appreciate it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.1333282471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_restroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "restroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.7999968212
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさん、ありがとうございます\n俺は何をすれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "miho-san‚ thank you\nAnd what should I do…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.4666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "何もしないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just do nothing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.9000029247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_restroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "restroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.7666695913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "髪型のオーダーは私がしておいたので\n{user}さんは黙っていればいいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've already ordered the hairstyle\nso {user}-san just need to keep quiet",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.2666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_restroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "restroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.733336258
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "カット中は絶対に一言も発さず余計なことは\nしないで下さい……いいですか？",
      "translations": {
